{"tid":345672,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「負能量100」好多朋友但好孤獨","createTime":"2017-08-03T09:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T15:45:31.000Z","uid":19923,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"00797cfc377098e59cc6e8ac6b9fae34e5de1eb9","tid":345672,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:23:33.000Z","msg":"有無人同我一樣，明明好多朋友但係覺得自己好孤獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然身邊有好多所謂朋友，但係永遠都覺得自己不被重視，成日起group講野約人無乜邊個會應，又或者個group入面既人之間會單對單msg，但係永遠無我份。個種感覺真係好難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我都係想被重視，被認同姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明大家一齊出黎玩個陣都好開心，我都好樂意咁扮下on9 tum大家開心，點解一返返日常生活就咁空虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 愈大對比就愈覺得孤獨。可能係我attention freak，但我驚我就黎有抑鬱症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d74000eff6e19bb0ba551d811a286ce5098286c6","tid":345672,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:24:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"219036361ba1fcb39bc1d096bbce19ade5800e3e","tid":345672,"uid":73349,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:25:46.000Z","msg":"有時啲野唔好太執著睇開啲個人會自在好多<br />\n雖然要做起黎唔容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079333e5b48b74441b51454f78a8e1b4dc64295a","tid":345672,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:25:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9a17c6e7f324c2817aa491438e07f1b516e1dd","tid":345672,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:28:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rLuXe_GPHEU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrLuXe_GPHEU&d=bh7oF2kDHXzgNtmcBx0XUU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=5aee070f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rLuXe_GPHEU</a>送首歌俾大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a22703aa4c0387edfe263f294958d114b77f32","tid":345672,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:30:44.000Z","msg":"作詞：小寒<br />\n作曲：方大同<br />\n編曲：Edward Chan/方大同<br />\n監製：Edward Chan/Charles Lee/方大同<br />\n<br />\n歡笑聲　歡呼聲<br />\n炒熱氣氛　心卻很冷<br />\n聚光燈　是種蒙恩<br />\n我卻不能　喊等一等<br />\n<br />\n我真佩服我　還能幽默<br />\n掉眼淚時　用笑掩過<br />\n怕人看破　顧慮好多<br />\n不談寂寞　我們就都快活<br />\n<br />\n我不唱聲嘶力竭的情歌<br />\n不表示沒有心碎的時刻<br />\n我不曾攤開傷口任宰割<br />\n癒合　就無人曉得　我內心挫折<br />\n活像個孤獨患者　自我拉扯<br />\n外向的孤獨患者　有何不可<br />\n<br />\n笑越大聲　越是殘忍<br />\n擠滿體溫　室溫更冷<br />\n萬一關燈　空虛擾人<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=bh7oF2kDHXzgNtmcBx0XUU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=ded87380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a>　魔鏡歌詞網 <br />\n我卻不能　喊等一等<br />\n<br />\n你說你愛我　卻一直說<br />\n說我不該　窩在角落<br />\n策劃逃脫　這也有錯<br />\n連我脆弱　的權利都掠奪<br />\n<br />\n我不唱聲嘶力竭的情歌<br />\n不表示沒有心碎的時刻<br />\n我不曾攤開傷口任宰割<br />\n癒合　就無人曉得　我內心挫折<br />\n活像個孤獨患者　自我拉扯<br />\n外向的孤獨患者　有何不可<br />\n<br />\n我不要聲嘶力竭的情歌<br />\n來提示我需要你的時刻<br />\n表面鎮定並不是保護色<br />\n反而　是要你懂得　我不知為何<br />\n活像個孤獨患者　自我拉扯<br />\n外向的孤獨患者　需要認可"},{"pid":"3c256172c1629d394588f6b693c5e898ac58f1fe","tid":345672,"uid":19923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:31:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時啲野唔好太執著睇開啲個人會自在好多<br />\n雖然要做起黎唔容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我淨係想講完野有人理下渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1414c35b2e2e8692125cf6dcc69413b93ad09b","tid":345672,"uid":55823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:31:52.000Z","msg":"咁同冇朋友有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae50ab618db482379f5b969db1ab24a0295a024","tid":345672,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:32:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁同冇朋友有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一路都無真係會care你既朋友好難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9b8ded376d74c378ff64d6dca50397e550765f","tid":345672,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:33:30.000Z","msg":"平時我起成班人之中係個超級開心果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能係咁所以無人會理我感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4728d4197d448c4dedb53a498ae42d317ef420","tid":345672,"uid":73349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:35:35.000Z",