:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已經睇化咗 中同group人已經少 仲要各自熟/有聯絡<br />\n講就話兄弟 出到嚟對住你根本冇嘢傾/唔想傾<br />\n好彩有個好錫我嘅女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉我都係，但係人除左另一半都需要朋友嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a44ed87ca60cf292a06de7ecb77d8f20c7023160","tid":345672,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac107d05119a1a245288d3757a6439ca206a7816","tid":345672,"uid":132829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:44:57.000Z","msg":"小圈子 永遠冇自己份<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f6ed4f21ddea18ed67a480da2e17840d872b81","tid":345672,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:45:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小圈子 永遠冇自己份<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f648f7d3995726b51b0ed516952a87f03c2b35","tid":345672,"uid":18230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:45:55.000Z","msg":"唔好太著重某一班朋友，你個圈子唔會只有佢地架嘛"},{"pid":"baf7c0e2c1353af0c678ebcb44fd71dc3285656d","tid":345672,"uid":128277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:48:25.000Z","msg":"試下msg下人地囉<br />\n以前我都會諗點解大grp冇人應又咁多小圈子gathering，係咪同佢地唔夠熟，又唔敢講，其實大家都係咁諗，冇人做第一步<br />\n不過我都唔係成日主動搵人，所以依家有時被忘記我都可以接受既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8928dc6ad64f7914ef401b55981ec0f520913ca","tid":345672,"uid":73349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:48:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已經睇化咗 中同group人已經少 仲要各自熟/有聯絡<br />\n講就話兄弟 出到嚟對住你根本冇嘢傾/唔想傾<br />\n好彩有個好錫我嘅女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉我都係，但係人除左另一半都需要朋友嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無呢班咪搵過另一班，呢個世界無話無左邊個唔得。同埋記住唔係你唔好，係你同果班人唔夾姐。<br />\n識多啲人，總會搵到志同道合岩嘴型既朋友。"},{"pid":"9e6841c2d8491317352fd1f63be06d318c7782c2","tid":345672,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T10:15:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好太著重某一班朋友，你個圈子唔會只有佢地架嘛</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb8139476476b308ccc221596da9433395ddc96","tid":345672,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T10:16:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下msg下人地囉<br />\n以前我都會諗點解大grp冇人應又咁多小圈子gathering，係咪同佢地唔夠熟，又唔敢講，其實大家都係咁諗，冇人做第一步<br />\n不過我都唔係成日主動搵人，所以依家有時被忘記我都可以接受既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都成日主動起group到講野，但係一無人理我就會好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 令我唔想再主動受傷"},{"pid":"68df9e660fac15c7ea5269bfdbfb825057f62acb","tid":345672,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T10:17:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已經睇化咗 中同group人已經少 仲要各自熟/有聯絡<br />\n講就話兄弟 出到嚟對住你根本冇嘢傾/唔想傾<br />\n好彩有個好錫我嘅女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉我都係，但係人除左另一半都需要朋友嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無呢班咪搵過另一班，呢個世界無話無左邊個唔得。同埋記住唔係你唔好，係你同果班人唔夾姐。<br />\n識多啲人，總會搵到志同道合岩嘴型既朋友。</blockquote><br />\n怪就怪在出到黎大家都好開心，但係背後其實成日俾人忽略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}